author: AddictedToStyrene
title: Minfig
review:
Came with a Chupa Chups lollipop in a sealed plastic egg. The only way to tell what figure you got was to break the seal - hopefully you bought it first. They started at $6 Australian, but after a couple of months stores were letting trays of eggs go for a few dollars.

This set had one figure, no other Lego.

author: hustla187
title: China Girl
review: This is an exotic based minifig which I like. Also, you could get this and save about 60 dollars getting the set that the minifig is in. I really think this is a cool minifig, and is a good way to get it.
